# Generated pipeline data. On `main` none of this is tracked:
#   - data/events/*.json : rebuildable projection (regenerated each build)
#   - data/geocache.json : transient cache
#   - data/raw, data/state : durable store — lives on the `data` branch, not main
data/events/*.json
data/geocache.json
data/raw/
data/state/
